'''Muscle maggots''' were burrowing maggots native to the planet [[Rattatak/Legends|Rattatak]] that entered their victims' bodies and crawled through their muscle tissue, causing extreme pain. The maggots were used for [[Torture/Legends|torture]] purposes, particularly by [[Asajj Ventress/Legends|Asajj Ventress]] on [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan Kenobi]]. Over time, the extended pain that the muscle maggot generated made prisoners lose muscle strength, providing for easier interrogation.

